<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/12788665-a-blaze-of-glory"><img alt="A Blaze of Glory (Civil War: 1861-1865, Western Theater, #1)" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1330952316l/12788665._SX98_.jpg" />
